learnt more about firebase and the use of firebase .
firebase provides a real time database and the backend as a service.
it also provides secure file uploads and downloads for apps regardless of the network quality.
the tables in the database for both student and professor  was created in order to store the details of the student and professor.
the student table contains the information about the fields of student's first name, last name ,section ,semester , usn , department , email id and password.
the professor table contains the information about the fields of professor's first name , last name , professor id ,department ,email id and password.
